      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "走API v1，我们有个专门的端点。前端调用POST /journeys/{FinTech_LedgerService}/mint-badge，这里的FinTech_LedgerService是路径参数，标识具体的账本服务。然后API再跟Solana devnet交互。",
