    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把结构画出来：User到Frontend是完成任务，Frontend到API v1是POST请求，API v1再到Solana devnet发交易。这样三层架构对吗？",
